<head>
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
<title>管理員資料新增 - addEmp.jsp</title>

<style>
table#table-1 {
	background-color: #CCCCFF;
	border: 2px solid black;
	text-align: center;
}

table#table-1 h4 {
	color: red;
	display: block;
	margin-bottom: 1px;
}

h4 {
	color: blue;
	display: inline;
}
</style>

<style>
table {
	width: 450px;
	background-color: white;
	margin-top: 1px;
	margin-bottom: 1px;
}

table, th, td {
	border: 0px solid #CCCCFF;
}

th, td {
	padding: 1px;
}
</style>

